OL,6,FThe case detailing the charges against
OL,7,Fthe Democratic politician is sealed,
OL,8,Fso it is not clear what laws Adams is
OL,9,Faccused of breaking or when he might
OL,10,Fhave to appear in court.
OL,12,FThe US attorney's office in Manhattan
OL,13,Fdeclined to comment.
OL,15,FFederal investigators had seized
OL,16,FAdams' electronic devices nearly a
OL,17,Fyear ago as part of an investigation
OL,18,Ffocused on whether Adams conspired
OL,19,Fwith the Turkish government to funnel
OL,20,Fillegal foreign donations into his
OL,21,Felectoral campaign.
