OL,6,FBecause the charges were sealed, it
OL,7,Fwas unknown whether they dealt with
OL,8,Fthose same matters.
OL,10,FOn Monday, the New York Times reported
OL,11,Fthat prosecutors subpoenaed the
OL,12,Fmayor's office for information related
OL,13,Fto five other countries - Israel,
OL,14,FChina, Qatar, South Korea and
OL,15,FUzbekistan.
OL,17,FAdams, a former police captain, was
OL,18,Felected to mayor of New York three
OL,19,Fyears ago and at the time stressed his
OL,20,Fcommitment to public safety.
