OL,6,FIn the past two weeks, the leaders he
OL,7,Fappointed to oversee the country's
OL,8,Flargest police force and largest
OL,9,Fschools system have announced their
OL,10,Fresignations.
OL,12,FAdams is the first mayor in New York
OL,13,FCity history to be indicted while in
OL,14,Foffice.
OL,16,FIf he were to resign, he would be
OL,17,Freplaced by the city's public
OL,18,Fadvocate, Jumaane Williams, who would
OL,19,Fthen schedule a special election.
