OL,6,FGovernor Kathy Hochul has the power to
OL,7,Fremove Adams from office. Hochul
OL,8,Fspokesperson, Avi Small, issued a
OL,9,Fstatement late on Wednesday that said
OL,10,F"Governor Hochul is aware of these
OL,11,Fconcerning news reports and is
OL,12,Fmonitoring the situation.
OL,14,F"It would be premature to comment
OL,15,Ffurther until the matter is confirmed
OL,16,Fby law enforcement."
